LanguageData.ARA_ResearchTab.generalTitle: Exploration of the evolution of Arachne insect group
LanguageData.ARA_ResearchTab.generalDescription: By exploring and improving the life forms of the Arachne Bugs, you will be able to hatch more powerful individuals and create insect swarm equipment such as more advanced weapons.\n\nResearch on this technology tree can only be done by the Arachne Bugs!
